    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p><i>6th-level College of Eloquence feature</i></p><p>You have gained the ability to make your speech intelligible to any creature. As an action, choose one or more creatures within 60 feet of you, up to a number equal to your Charisma modifier (minimum of one creature). The chosen creatures can magically understand you, regardless of the language you speak, for 1 hour.</p><p>Once you use this feature, you can't use it again until you finish a long rest, unless you expend a spell slot to use it again.</p></div>",
